        <a href="Hive+on+Spark%253A+Join+Design+Master#page-metadata-end" class="assistive">Skip to end of metadata</a>
<div id="page-metadata-start" class="assistive"></div>

    <div class="page-metadata">
        <ul>
            <li class="page-metadata-modification-info">
                
        
    
        
    
        
        
            Created by <span class='author'>     <a href="https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/~szehon"
                       class="url fn"
                            >Szehon Ho</a></span>, last modified on <a class='last-modified' title='Jan 13, 2015 01:00' href='https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/pages/diffpagesbyversion.action?pageId=50858744&amp;selectedPageVersions=8&amp;selectedPageVersions=9'>Jan 13, 2015</a>
